Package: gfiExtremes
Type: Package
Title: Generalized Fiducial Inference for Extremes
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Stéphane", "Laurent", role = c("aut", "cre"), 
           email = "laurent_step@outlook.fr"),
    person("Jan", "Hannig", role = "aut"),
    person("Damian", "V. Wandler", role = "aut")
  )
Maintainer: Stéphane Laurent <laurent_step@outlook.fr>
Description: Fiducial framework to perform inference on the parameters and the extreme quantiles of the generalized Pareto distribution, assuming the threshold is a known or unknown parameter. Reference: Damian V. Wandler & Jan Hannig (2012) <doi:10.1007/s10687-011-0127-9>.
License: GPL (>= 2)
Depends: coda
Imports: Rcpp (>= 1.0.5), ismev, parallel, doParallel, foreach, stats
LinkingTo: Rcpp, BH, RcppArmadillo
Encoding: UTF-8
RoxygenNote: 7.1.1
